flowchart TD
    Start([Admin logs in]) --> Dash[Dashboard:<br/>orders, revenue, subscriptions, low-stock]
    Dash --> New[New order notification]
    New --> List[Open order management]
    List --> View[View order detail:<br/>items, customer, payment]

    View --> Decide{Process or cancel?}
    Decide -- Cancel --> Cancel[Set status = Cancelled<br/>restock items if needed]
    Cancel --> NotiCx[Notify customer] --> End2([Order closed])

    Decide -- Process --> S1[Confirmed]
    S1 --> S2[Preparing]
    S2 --> S3[Shipped]
    S3 --> AssignD[Create delivery + assign rider<br/>see Flow 7]
    AssignD --> S4[Delivered<br/>set by rider on completion]

    S1 --> N1[Notify customer at each change]
    S2 --> N1
    S3 --> N1
    S4 --> N1
    S4 --> Done[Enables customer review] --> End([Fulfilled])

    Note[Allowed transitions: Pending to Confirmed to Preparing<br/>to Shipped to Delivered. Delivered is set by the rider.]
    List -.-> Note
